 Гн    DIGITAL CAP:                                                          оГ
 Гн    ФФФФФФФФФФФФ                                                          оГ
 Гн    This includes any real digital source that didn't pass through any    оГ
 Гн    analog interface between the source (Sat/Antenna/Cable) and the file  оГ
 Гн    on your computer.                                                     оГ
 Гн                                                                          оГ
 Гн    This includes ATSC off-air antenna signals carrying MPEG2 Transport   оГ
 Гн    Streams (using cards such as MyHD/Hipix/WinTV-HD), DirecTiVo MPEG2    оГ
 Гн    Streams (not standard TiVo!) and DVB Stream Capture cards.            оГ
 Гн                                                                          оГ
 Гн                                                                          оГ
 Гн    *HDTV* (High Definition Televison): Digital recording from a source   оГ
 Гн           stream at either 1080i or 720p at a bitrate from 19,39mbps or  оГ
 Гн           higher.                                                        оГ
 Гн                                                                          оГ
 Гн                                                                          оГ
 Гн    *PDTV* (Pure Digital Television): Other resolution digital recor-     оГ
 Гн           dings from source streams at a bitrate of 10+mbps or higher.   оГ
 Гн           - This includes digital recordings from digital C-Band and     оГ
 Гн             DVB.                                                         оГ
 Гн                                                                          оГ
 Гн                                                                          оГ
 Гн    *SDTV* (Standard Digital Television): Digital recording or capture    оГ
 Гн           from a source stream at any resolution with bitrate under      оГ
 Гн           10mbps.                                                        оГ
 Гн           - This includes DirecTiVo but also captures from digisat or    оГ
 Гн             digicable with analog capture cards.                         оГ
 Гн                                                                          оГ
 Гн                                                                          оГ
 Гн    note: For SVCD, analog cable and antenna caps are not allowed, so     оГ
 Гн          SDTV is the lowest allowed source and will have no label. See   оГ
 Гн          NAMING below.                                                   оГ
 Гн                                                                          оГ
 Гн                                                                          оГ
 Гн    note: HDTV and PDTV rips are digital recordings, although PDTV was    оГ
 Гн          labeled wrongly in the past by some groups (TiVo is NOT PDTV).  оГ
 Гн                                                                          оГ
 Гн                                                                          оГ
 Гн    ANALOG CAP:                                                           оГ
 Гн    ФФФФФФФФФФФ                                                           оГ
 Гн    This includes any source that went through at least one Digital ->    оГ
 Гн    Analog -> Digital process.                                            оГ
 Гн                                                                          оГ
 Гн    This includes Standard TiVo, any MPEG2 capture card, any DV source    оГ
 Гн    (unless you're releasing your home videos that were actually shot on  оГ
 Гн    a DV camera) or any other standard capture card.                      оГ
 Гн                                                                          оГ
 Гн                                                                          оГ
 Гн    PDVTV and HDTV is NEVER captured in analogue, on the other hand a     оГ
 Гн    SDTV cap can be both.                                                 оГ
