 Гн    COMMENTS:                                                             оГ
 Гн    ФФФФФФФФФ                                                             оГ
 Гн    For SVCD/DivX, any video, regardless of Analog or Digital should be   оГ
 Гн    converted to 23.976fps (NTSC) or 25fps (PAL) "Progressive Film" for   оГ
 Гн    correct encoding.                                                     оГ
 Гн    A LOT of group don't bother with this step and thus their encoding    оГ
 Гн    quality suffers, regardless of their source quality.                  оГ
 Гн                                                                          оГ
 Гн    Even if your source video comes as Progressive 59.976fps (as it can   оГ
 Гн    with ATSC sources), you must still convert to the proper frame rate   оГ
 Гн    or your video will be jerky or waste bits.                            оГ
 Гн                                                                          оГ
 Гн    For any NTSC encode (other than live shows like the "Tonight Show")   оГ
 Гн    the video must be converted to 23.976fps through the use of IVTC or   оГ
 Гн    duplicate frame elimination (for ATSC 59.976fps progressive sources)  оГ
 Гн    prior to SVCD encoding. And once encoded, you must enable the 3:2     оГ
 Гн    pulldown flag to enable playback at 29.976fps (even though the sour-  оГ
 Гн    ce still remains at 23.976fps).                                       оГ
 Гн                                                                          оГ
 Гн    Analog Cable or Analog Antenna rips on SVCD are NOT allowed.          оГ
